"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-06-15-Family-keeps-The-Beast-going-says-Olympic-champion-sprinter-Blake-1urPqznlVAY-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Yohan Blake of Jamaica will participate in the 2024 Paris Summer Olympic Games after winning two 4x100-meter men's relay gold medals.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 242, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999987314823, \"rank\": 1.2614349964890737e-09, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with CGTN Sports Scene's Zhu Mandan, he said that family keeps him going as one of the best sprinters in the world.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2987352542723344e-21, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan\", \"score\": 0.9954741424816291, \"rank\": 0.004546434031048145, \"text\": \"Mandan\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, many times I look at it as close to 20 something years in training.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What kept me going is my family.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not just run from me,\\\" Blake said.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nicknamed 'The Beast', 34-year-old Blake will race at his fourth edition of the Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999980913117, \"rank\": 1.9086911209977306e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said it will be his final Olympics.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympics come every four years.\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And you know, you want to start your family and you want to live a life as well, apart from track.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not want to be there running that long,\\\" Blake said.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So this is my last one.\\\"\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In his first Olympic Games in London in 2012, Blake emerged as a serious challenger for his compatriot Usain Bolt in the men's 100-meter and 200-meter events.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998507531320907, \"rank\": 0.0001492147904805936, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end, Blake got the silver medal in both.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"score\": 0.9866888277197884, \"rank\": 0.01348797341483769, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bolt spoke highly of Blake, especially about his hard work in training.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Easily, easily.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could say that.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Very easy,\\\" Blake said when asked if he thinks he trained harder than Bolt.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also misses the rivalry with Bolt, who has retired.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's fun at the same time.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's tough at the same time because, you know, we are pushing each other,\\\" Blake told Zhu.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not want to lose.\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not want to lose.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do miss it.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese sprinter Su Bingtian finished the men's 100-meter semifinals in 9.83 seconds at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021, setting his personal best and becoming the first Chinese sprinter to qualify for the final of the event.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5758946518796092, \"rank\": 0.7360601913310157, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Bingtian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Su Bingtian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Bingtian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Bingtian\"}, {\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5758946518796092, \"rank\": 0.7360601913310157, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Su and Blake have known each other for a long time since they competed with each other in London in 2012.\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998507531320907, \"rank\": 0.0001492147904805936, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have known Su from my first Olympics in London,\\\" Blake said.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2021, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998507531320907, \"rank\": 0.0001492147904805936, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Me and Su were in the same race.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Me and Su have been running from when we were little.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I look up to Su as a really great athlete and I just want to say, keep working hard Su.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe in you.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know you have done so many things for China.\\\"\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9979776644728001, \"rank\": 0.001025840178195053, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about his goal for Paris 2024, Blake said there is no goal but a dream, which is to finish on top.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2331, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"score\": 0.9866888277197884, \"rank\": 0.01348797341483769, \"text\": \"Blake\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Blake\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": []}]}"